Georgette Nkoma (amụrụ na abalị iri na isii, na onwa isii, na afọ 1965) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba ọsọ

Na afọ 1996 African Championships ọ ritere ihe nrite ọla edo na mita 100 na 200. O mekwara asọmpi na World Championships na afọ 1993, 1995 na 1997, yana na 4 × 100 m relay na 1996 Summer Olympics n'erughị nke ikpeazụ.
